INSTALL:
1. Download: https://github.com/downloads/GabeStah/QuestPointer_KulldamFix/QuestPointer.zip
2. Unzip into World of Warcraft/Interface/Addons
3. Run World of Warcraft and enjoy!

USAGE:
QuestPointer_KulldamFix is a slight modification to the QuestPointer addon by Kemayo (http://www.wowace.com/addons/questpointer/), and includes a minor bug fix to the waypoint system.